sections.heading: Sections; supplementary to existing law
sections.text: Sections 31-727 to 31-762 are supplementary to existing statutes and confer upon sanitary and improvement districts powers not heretofore granted and sections 31-727 to 31-762 shall not be construed as repealing or amending any existing statute.SourceLaws 1949
